Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.90,0:01:54.00,OP CN,,0,0,0,,Revolution
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.00,0:01:55.00,OP CN,,0,0,0,,Revolution
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.00,0:01:56.00,OP CN,,0,0,0,,Revolution
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.10,0:01:59.50,OP CN,,0,0,0,,由你和我们 一起来革命吧 Start
